name: 4th International Conference on Mental Health & Psychiatry
content: Mental Health 2020 invites all the participants and attendees from all over the world to attend 4th Edition of International Conference on Mental Health & Psychiatry during July 15-16, 2020 to be held at Vienna, Austria with the Theme: Emerging new involvements in the field of Mental Health which includes prompt Keynote Presentations, Oral talks, Poster Presentations, Workshop, Symposia and Exhibitions. Website: https://mentalhealthconference.euroscicon.com/ Contact email: mentalhealth@meetingsemail.com
